        "created_at": "2022-05-18T00:27:19.373Z",
        "cooked": "<p>We are running FDB v6.2.27.</p>\n<p>Both the source and destination clusters are 2-region/3-DC clusters. Not sure if DR works between 2-region clusters.</p>\n<p>So our current 3-DC clusters have redundancy already. Our purpose to use DR is for migrating FDB clusters to another platform with min downtime and for setting up an additional location for applications to read (using <code>READ_LOCK_AWARE</code> option).</p>",
